(329, 12, 'home_text_content', '<p>\r\n                        Imboxo lets you stream movies from creators you love while you discover unique products curated by passionate fans. Shop and watch, and get unlimited rewards . We don\'t just entertain, we empower – artists get rewarded on every play, and shoppers earn exclusive benefits.\r\n                        </p>\r\n                        <p>\r\n                            Join us in building global movie markets that fuel dreams, yours and your audience\'s. Get entertained, get Imboxo!\r\n                        </p>'),
