(339, 12, 'home_about_big_text', 'Originally my idea for Internet Movie Box Office was to help movies find great audiences easily and for Audiences to find great movies. <br><br>\r\n                    Wether you are an IMBOXO CREATOR OR A USER or both, I want to personally welcome you to the begining of this transparent journey where literally MOVIE CREATORS and USERS can discover each other without the standard frustrations associated with making movies and trying to find great movies to watch.<br><br>\r\n                    \r\n                    Please keep in mind IMBOXO is just now starting to reach out to CREATORS to let them know of the IMBOXO service.  As Creators begin to learn of the service they will upload their movies their way to their own IMBOXO BOX OFFICES which you can follow and purchase just the movies you want to watch.<br><br>\r\n                    \r\n                    IMBOXO really is a whole new way for Creators and Users to interact and I am excited for all of us.<br><br>\r\n                    Sincerely<br><br>'),
(340, 12, '_home_about_big_text', 'field_65aa04446de7a'),
