(1092, 12, 'explore_text', 'Western'),
(1093, 12, 'question', 'How can I make money on your platform?'),
(1094, 12, 'answer', 'There are two main ways:<br>\r\n                            As a movie creator: Upload your films and get paid every time someone watches them! We share a percentage of every purchase made through your content with you, directly supporting your artistic endeavors.<br>\r\n                            As a shopper: Earn reward points with every purchase, which you can use to buy further movies, merchandise, or even subscribe to exclusive creator content. The more you shop, the more you get rewarded!'),
(1095, 12, 'block_number', '(01)'),
(1096, 12, 'question', 'How does the shop-and-watch feature work?'),
(1097, 12, 'answer', 'Discover movies and shows on our platform. When you see something you like and want to watch, explore the associated merchandise and products featured alongside it. Buy something while watching, and a portion of that purchase goes directly back to the creator of the content you\'re enjoying. It\'s a unique way to show your appreciation and help them keep making great movies!'),
(1098, 12, 'block_number', '(02)'),
(1099, 12, 'question', 'What kind of rewards can I earn through shopping?'),
(1100, 12, 'answer', 'Our reward system offers various benefits, including:<br>\r\n                          Points that can be redeemed for movie purchases, merchandise, and exclusive content.<br>\r\nEarly access to new releases and creator specials.<br>\r\nDiscounts on purchases and subscriptions.<br>\r\nPersonalized recommendations and curated shopping experiences.<br>\r\nBy shopping through our platform, you not only support your favorite creators, but also unlock a world of benefits for yourself!'),
(1101, 12, 'block_number', '(03)'),
